<doc id="638168" wikidata="Q4815871" url="?curid=638168" title="Atiyah">
<text>Atiyyah ( &quot;‘aṭiyyah&quot;), which generally implies &quot;something (money or goods given as regarded) received as a gift&quot; or also means &quot;present, gift, benefit, boon, favor, granting, giving&quot;&quot;.&quot;

The name is also spelt Atiyeh, Attiah, Attieh, Atieh, Atié, Atiya, Atiyya, Attiya, Attiyah, Attyé, Ateya, Attua, Ateah, Antuya, or Atia. 

It may refer to:
==Surname==
